name: ℭ𝔥𝔞𝔬𝔰 𝔦𝔫 ℑ 𝔞𝔫𝔡 ℌ𝔢𝔯
description: "The first that we've met eyes, I have always been.  In disarray, confused, lost. For what I had hoped in her, had never been. To dissipate the chaos, the chaos still stay. I have always wanted to veil the chaos from her. Who I am, I've ever been.  Hiding the reality comes with the difficulty. For the god of truth always planned a mutiny."
